title: Dillon Nathaniel
description:
HOUSE PARTY BRUNCH! Dillon Nathaniel takes control of Bergerac on Sunday, 7/21 for a day party you'll never forget. Dance on the furniture, go-go dance on the bar, do whatever it takes to have a good time! We'll have food, drinks, punchbowls and house music from one of the best djs in the game. Let's get a little wild ;)

Where? Bergerac, 316 11th st. (below Audio in the bespoke lounge)

When? 7/21 | 1-6pm

Dress it up, wear something cool, let's make this a vibe.

GA and VIP table options to choose from if you want to go the extra mile.

21+ event. All sales are final

Brought to you by All Day All Night + Dirty Not Sorry
